{"type": "article", "id": 33776, "title": "涂黑的红酒包装，想用神秘感吸引年轻人｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-10-26T23:25:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 34335, "name": "Boulon Blanc"}, {"id": 34336, "name": "Hundo"}, {"id": 34337, "name": "Co Partnership"}, {"id": 33366, "name": "goTenna"}, {"id": 34338, "name": "Ecomo Inc."}, {"id": 34339, "name": "Dror Kaspi"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 113, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161026204658TwmOrLBdvsnAFp0a.jpeg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Ecomo Bottle by Ecomo Inc.</h3><p>在外面喝水的时候，难免会担心水是否足够干净。为了让人们能够快捷地了解水质并进行简单的处理，来自美国加州的<a href=\"http://ecomo.io/\" rel=\"nofollow\">初创公司</a>研发了一款名为 Ecomo 的智能水壶。接近水壶底部的地方是一条可拆卸的水质监测手环，与壶中的传感器相连。把水倒入壶中轻摇，监测环就会通过三种颜色的灯光告诉你水质情况，同时还会监测你每天的喝水量。Ecomo 更特别的地方在于内置的三合一过滤装置，包含了活性碳纤维、离子交换纤维以及纳米纤维膜。只要扭一扭瓶底，滤芯就会对杂质进行过滤，让你喝到放心的水。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/ecomo/ecomo-the-worlds-first-bottle-that-tests-and-filte\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 139 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026170507m3KIcEMY0oGZLvgQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026170507JLH3s8rOfYFvUqyo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.979856\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026170507UgaxQhq83iyRbHYW.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.205882\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026170510sgVpvDW0cAfuoxUM.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561765\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026170507AkeX8CKuJTVb4yW6.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.888235\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026170508QpiHePMWX0SDdjt4.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Table by Boulon Blanc</h3><p>市面上大部分折叠桌采用的都是和熨衣板一样的 X 型结构，来自法国的设计团队 <a href=\"http://www.boulonblanc.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Boulon Blanc</a> 打算挑战这一常规的调节方式，让桌子变身的过程显得更加美观。设计师从航空学以及制表业中汲取灵感，以螺旋桨和机翼设计为基础，打造了像是回旋镖一样的桌腿结构。桌腿一端长一端短，让人联想到表盘上的分针和时针，两种高度下的结构都能保证稳定性。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/712852295/boulon-blanc-the-next-generation-of-transformable\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，桌子的最低价为 640 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026170438JVUDINEY7ynhQ3Ts.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.402941\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026170438XUGiyFnom0gbRaIt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.641176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026170438VFCLxlMBoytUOrsQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.779412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026170438jHkPwWtgydZ5UCN2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.608824\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026170438Q0dG8weYPgMmUBWj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.608824\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>goTenna Mesh by goTenna</h3><p>去户外游玩，在没有网络信号的时候，想联系同伴该怎么办？来自美国纽约的初创公司 <a href=\"http://gotenna.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">goTenna</a> 为此研发了一款名叫 goTenna Mesh 通讯工具，让你能够在没有信号的情况下也能沟通顺畅。它的外形很像是常用的 USB 网卡，通过蓝牙与手机相连后，手机就可以借助其内置的无线电波在一定范围（如果所处的区域宽敞，最远距离为 4.8 千米，拥挤区域最远可支持 1.6 千米的距离）内与同伴交流。配套的应用允许你们在手机上发送短信、GPS 定位甚至群聊，可以容纳一百条历史消息。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/gotenna/gotenna-mesh-off-grid-people-powered-connectivity\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，两个成套预订，最低价为 149 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610261750407powfPJh2DClAi8V.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.382353\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026175041oSrLMhzxEtYPlu1X.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.513235\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026175040xl5YhKQWP8q2tMTn.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.469118\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026175040nY7fQX0jRMrB5vVt.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.520240\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026175041UjtSNwRhvcI0i3FQ.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.487879\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Hundo by Henry &amp; Jack Madin</h3><p>来自澳大利亚墨尔本的 Henry 和 Jack Madin 两兄弟都是当地乐队 Harpoons 的成员，凭借着对音乐的热爱，喜欢动手制作新玩意儿的 Henry 创造了两款造型简单的智能木制乐器，并和 Jack 一起成立了 <a href=\"http://www.hundo.com.au/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hundo</a> 这一品牌。Hundo 基础款（Basic）是一个四格的电子鼓垫，另一款名为 Marimba，是一个没有固定音律设定的木琴，有九个可以随意设置的木制琴键。虽然这两种乐器都需要配套的木槌以及音频软件进行配合，在声音呈现上不受限制这一点还是为演奏提供了更大的发挥空间。如果你对这些乐器感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"http://www.hundo.com.au/store/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>进行购买，售价分别为 280 和 560 澳元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026170359gGsTQu5FkeqHymAW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.657895\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026170400GDS87ElWdgwrmVjJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026170359JnKiUdCMTF5AXaym.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.219737\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026170400CrMXJkqphZTb1Dts.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026170400hlvdC3FbwUGmHr0D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.657895\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610261704005WjgvIMAxeG3q70H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.657895\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>RELEASE by Dror Kaspi</h3><p>          </p><p>以混凝土制作的灯具并不少见，以色列设计师 <a href=\"http://www.ardomadesign.com/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dror Kaspi</a> 带来的这款 <a href=\"http://www.ardomadesign.com/release\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">RELEASE</a> 就是混凝土灯罩与铝制底座的结合。它看上去就像有一种无形的力量将坚硬的灰色圆柱体从正中央劈开，将里面暗藏的明亮光源展现出来，造型简单又很讨巧。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/463491686/release-concrete-table-lampbedside-lamp\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 131.26 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026201902w5FndYtu9BJKjZfO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026201903BDWnGk37mfER6YZP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.459144\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026201903NpEYdfHLexvGBkg7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498501\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>The Underground Project by Co Partnership</h3><p>          </p><p>越来越多的小众品牌通过在线销售这一渠道接触到了更多渴望看到差异化和个性化标签的年轻人。在“年轻化”这件事上，澳大利亚的老牌红酒商 <a href=\"http://www.hungerfordhill.com.au/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hungerford Hill</a> 委托创意机构 <a href=\"http://co-partnership.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Co Partnership</a> 为其设计了一条名为 <a href=\"http://www.hungerfordhill.com.au/shop/category/the-underground-project\" rel=\"nofollow\">The Underground Project</a> 的仅供网购的产品线。争取到更多对传统红酒包装并不感冒的年轻顾客，设计师打造了一套白底黑字、穿插了涂黑效果的的标签，给人一种仿佛来自地下酒庄的神秘感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026175915hy3GzqUTx9dZHYMj.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026175915SfwnmxEdGC4zKIAF.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026175915SHpR5a6KwMsVePTv.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161026175914ax3GysOeN0rIF642.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>"}